# ==============================================
# QUICK SETUP GUIDE
# ==============================================
#
# 1. Copy this file:
#    cp .env.example .env
#
# 2. Set up PostgreSQL database:
#    - Local: Install PostgreSQL and create 'eventease' database
#    - Cloud: Use Render, Railway, or Supabase
#
# 3. Update DATABASE_URL with your connection string
#
# 4. Generate NEXTAUTH_SECRET:
#    openssl rand -base64 32
#
# 5. Set NEXTAUTH_URL to your domain (or localhost for development)
#
# 6. Install dependencies:
#    npm install
#
# 7. Run database migrations:
#    npx prisma migrate dev
#
# 8. Seed the database:
#    npm run seed
#
# 9. Start the development server:
#    npm run dev
#
# ==============================================
